midnight-blue-description =
    Midnight Blue is the default FreeSynergy desktop theme.

    It uses deep navy and dark blue backgrounds with a vivid cyan accent color and
    crisp white text. Panels use a subtle glass-effect with soft shadows. The theme
    is designed for long work sessions in dimly lit or dark environments and reduces
    eye strain while keeping contrast high.

midnight-blue-features =
    - Deep navy and dark blue backgrounds
    - Vivid cyan accent color
    - Glass-effect panels with soft shadows
    - High contrast white text
    - Optimized for dark environments
    - Default FreeSynergy theme
